{"article_id":"pka7qUrbElnTYzfL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Reports had said","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"official","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"overseeing investigation of Russian election interference and links to Trump campaign","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"would resign","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"Deputy attorney general Rod Rosenstein remains in his job ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"after reports on Monday said","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"he had resigned","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"or offered to do so .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"The White House said","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Donald Trump and Rosenstein had \" an extended conversation \" about news stories","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"published last week","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"reporting","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"that Rosenstein discussed with colleagues secretly recording Trump","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"or having him removed from office .","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"The two plan to meet on Thursday , after the president ' s return from a United Nations general assembly meeting in New York ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"press secretary Sarah Sanders said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Sanders said","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"the meeting was at Rosenstein ' s request .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"The White House did not comment on reports","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Rosenstein expected to be fired imminently","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"or had resigned .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"The deputy attorney general oversees the investigation of Russian election interference and links between the Trump campaign and Moscow .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"The New York Times reported last week","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that he discussed secretly recording the president","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"and invoking the 25th amendment","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"to remove Trump from office .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Rosenstein said","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"the report was \" inaccurate \" .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Rod Rosenstein disputes report","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"he discussed removing Trump under 25th amendment","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"On Monday morning ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"as reports","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"of Rosenstein leaving his post","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"spread ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"a spokesperson for the Department of Justice declined to comment .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"If Rosenstein were to leave his job ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"it would throw into question the oversight of special counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Under the Department of Justice succession statute , solicitor general Noel Francisco would be left in charge of supervising Mueller ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"University of Texas law school professor Steve Vladeck has written .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"But Trump also might be able to appoint a temporary replacement on an \" acting \" basis for up to 210 days ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Vladeck writes","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"- that person would need to have passed Senate confirmation for another post","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"or be a senior official from a relevant department .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"As anticipation of Rosenstein ' s departure grew on Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Democrats in Congress and former federal prosecutors called on Republicans to speak out in favor","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"of protecting the Mueller investigation .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"\" Congress must take immediate steps , \"","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"said Representative Val Demings of Florida in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"\" Time to protect the Mueller investigation .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Now , \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"tweeted Preet Bharara , former US attorney for the southern district of New York .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Trump and 'collusion ' :","depth":3},{"id":53,"text":"what we know so far about Mueller 's Russia investigation","depth":3},{"id":54,"text":"Read more","depth":3},{"id":55,"text":"Rosenstein was overseeing Mueller ' s work","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"after the attorney general , Jeff Sessions , recused himself due to his contacts with Russian officials","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"when he was part of the Trump campaign .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Trump has repeatedly attacked Sessions for that move .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"In overseeing the special counsel ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Rosenstein is responsible","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"for approving major new directions in the investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"for signing off on the budget","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"and for meeting regularly with Mueller","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"to assess the investigation ' s progress .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"For more than a year , Trump has railed against the Russia investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"calling it a \" witch hunt \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and accusing the prosecutors involved","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"- many of whom , like Rosenstein and Mueller , are Republicans -","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"of harboring ulterior partisan motives .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Trump ' s relationship with Rosenstein has been vexed .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"The president has tweeted","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that Rosenstein is \" weak \"","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"but in August he also said","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"the relationship was \" fantastic \" .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Frustration moved in both directions ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"with Rosenstein reportedly growing \" angry \" at Trump in May 2017 ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"after Trump used a memo","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"written by Rosenstein","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"to justify the firing of FBI director James Comey .","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"It was in the sensitive aftermath of that firing","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"that Rosenstein suggested recording the president ,","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"the Times reported .","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"One source told the Times","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"Rosenstein had suggested recording the president \" sarcastically \" ' ;","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"others said","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"he was serious .","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"Sources for the Times report included people familiar with memos","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"kept by former FBI deputy director Andrew McCabe about his conversations with Rosenstein .","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"McCabe was fired by Trump in March ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"days before he was due to retire .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"How many of Donald Trump 's advisers have been convicted ?","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":93,"text":"In a statement on Monday , amid speculation","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"that McCabe desired to undercut Rosenstein","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"- his onetime superior at the justice department","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"who played a direct role in the firing of McCabe ' s former boss , Comey -","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"McCabe denied any hand","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"in leaking the contents of his memos to the media .","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"\" To be clear ,","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"I had no role","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"in providing information of any kind to the media stories about events","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"following director Comey ' s firing , \"","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"McCabe said .","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"The 25th amendment ,","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"which was ratified after the assassination of John F Kennedy ,","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"provides for various paths of presidential succession ,","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"including in case","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"of the president being deemed \" unable to discharge the powers and duties of his office \" by the vice-president and a majority of cabinet officers .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"At a briefing","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"to talk about the UN general assembly ,","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"top foreign policy officials were peppered with questions about Rosenstein and the 25th amendment .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"\" Literally , I have never been in the White House","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"when that conversation has happened , \"","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"said the US envoy to the UN , Nikki Haley .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"\" I ' m not aware of any cabinet members","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"that are even talking about that .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"It is completely and totally absurd . \"","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Secretary of state Mike Pompeo added :","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"\" There was no discussion with me about the 25th amendment ,","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"so you can now report","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"that there were two senior leaders","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"who said","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"your question is ludicrous . \"","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":247,"left":177,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":175,"right":176,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":154,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":30,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":144,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":131,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":127,"right":130,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":0,"right":126,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":1,"right":2,"